&lt;p&gt;Conseguir de forma automática os simbolos de todas as ações IBOVESPA&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Aplicativo para construir Wordcloud</title><link>https://gomesfellipe.github.io/projects/appwordcloud/</link><pubDate>Sat, 07 Apr 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://gomesfellipe.github.io/projects/appwordcloud/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://gomesfellipe.shinyapps.io/appPCAkmeans/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img
